          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".A D2-(18-O) sample of 12.9 g with 95.1% enriched in",
                " 18-O and 98.5% enriched in D2, and a natural D2-Onat",
                " sample of 12 g were used to make corrections for",
                " background arising from free gamma-ray spectrum of",
                " 18-O(n,g)19-O reaction. A D2-(18-O) sample was used",
                " instead of a H2-(18-O) sample because H-2(n,g)H-3",
                " cross section is much lower than that of H-1(n,g)H-2,",
                " to measure the gamma-ray spectrum with a good signal-",
                " to-noise ratio. These samples were contained in a",
                " cylindrical case made of Lucite."
              ]
            }
          ],
